s/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於美國最終會否採取行動？劉兆佳直言，美國可能在報告中，用相當嚴厲的措辭以及非常強硬的態度，來表示對中央政府處理香港事務的高度不滿，但採取實質行動的可能性並不高<br />\n<br />\n現在，中央政府已經下定決心要整治香港亂局，維護國家安全，守衛香港管治權，這一點不會因為美國做什麼而改變。一旦中央政府開始反攻，不惜一切代價來保衛國家主權的時候，美國就會逐步陷入被動。"},{"pid":"0feb0d21c257ed1fd999b5c6af21e5223b90e17b","tid":2158994,"uid":219488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:40:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">[/b]你看看俄羅斯、委內瑞拉、伊朗、北韓等[/b]</span>"},{"pid":"107449211fb639b16607ff6028486ce157686547","tid":2158994,"uid":165881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"送返佢地d仔女返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683d4e2de2bbc7a5326237a372ecdde485240514","tid":2158994,"uid":56819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96901c1fd8b3dce02b575848b916ef0991cbf3bb","tid":2158994,"uid":63154,"like":76,"dislike":3,"score":73,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">你看看俄羅斯、委內瑞拉、伊朗、北韓等，一定有辦法保護自己官員。整個國家的實力怎可能照顧不到個別官員，否則便很麻煩，以後找人做高官或領導人都會出現困難。</span><br />\n<br />\n佢咁自信咁話要效法呢堆國家，我聽落都好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"即係中國經濟會步俄羅斯、委內瑞拉、伊朗、北韓後塵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707834ea0b9424de9c8189d0c4ca28853e50eb06","tid":2158994,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T06:48:17.000Z","msg":"無影響就唔好咁嬲咁care啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明既"},{"pid":"5b7672962a332a18889204414b9c5203efe91895","tid":2158994,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972fb89691bd5ab0d64c3bb2ebb5f516ba0b7eb6","tid":2158994,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f564227e1d8fa21fbc902c84b8c77aa4c6d670","tid":2158994,"uid":340081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"r